# Cloudflare Pages _redirects — used by the edge router.
# `200` preserves the browser URL (no visible rewrite), just serves
# the specified file. This matches the local Flask dev server's
# behaviour in server.py.

# Vanity user profile URLs: /u/<nickname> → /u/index.html
# Nickname is parsed from location.pathname by the page JS.
/u/*    /u/index.html    200
